			<title>B : GCB Card Offerings &amp; Types of Cards</title>
			<link>http://www.gcb.com.gh/products-services/electronic-banking/b-gcb-card-offerings-types-of-cards</link>
			<guid isPermaLink="true">http://www.gcb.com.gh/products-services/electronic-banking/b-gcb-card-offerings-types-of-cards</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[<div class="feed-description"><p><strong>Types of Cards</strong></p>
<p>GCB currently offers un-embossed range of MasterCard Debit card products. These cards turn good deals into great ones by adding value to both large or small purchases and cash withdrawals with convenience, protection, and enhanced benefits.</p>
<p><strong>GCB Card Offerings</strong></p>
<p>GCB currently offers three kinds of GCB MasterCard Debit cards. These are:</p>
<ul>
<li>Gold Debit Card</li>
<li>Standard Debit Card</li>
<li>Corporate Debit Card</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Gold Debit Card:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>High and secured personal spending limits</li>
<li>Can be used both locally and internationally</li>
<li>Accepted worldwide on ATM's and POS devices with MasterCard/Cirrus/Maestro sign(s).</li>
<li>Can be used for easy payments and cash withdrawals</li>
<li>Access to internet banking services (Commernet Plus)</li>
<li>Access to enhanced services from GCB and MasterCard</li>
<li>Secured flexible transactions</li>
<li>Suitable for high net worth individuals</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Standard Debit Card:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Secured personal spending limits</li>
<li>Can be used both locally and internationally</li>
<li>Accepted worldwide on ATM's and POS devices with MasterCard/Cirrus/Maestro sign(s).</li>
<li>Can be used for easy payments and cash withdrawals</li>
<li>Access to internet banking services (Commernet Plus)</li>
<li>Secured flexible transactions</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Corporate Debit Card:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Spending limits as authorized by institution or company</li>
<li>Issued to authorized individuals only</li>
<li>Can be used both locally and internationally</li>
<li>Accepted worldwide on ATM's and POS devices with MasterCard/Cirrus/Maestro sign(s).</li>
<li>Can be used for easy payments and cash withdrawals</li>
<li>Access to internet banking services (Commernet Plus)</li>
<li>Access to enhanced services from GCB and MasterCard</li>
<li>Clear statements for reconciliation</li>
<li>Secured flexible transactions</li>
</ul>
<p>Immediately your card is lost or stolen, please contact:</p>
<p>GCB Electronic Banking Call Centre<br />Tel: +233 . 21 . 246025 or +233 . 21. 254101; Fax: +233 . 21 . 246032<br />Email: mastercard@gcb.com.gh</p></div>]]></description>
